  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to EOG</title>

    <para>
      <application>EOG</application> is an application used for
      viewing and cataloging image files on the
      <application>GNOME</application> Desktop. It also has basic editing
      capabilites.
    </para>

    &lfs101_checked;

